title: Icarus [Good Omens Animatic]
author: Magismol-v
comment:
God's narration: 
Aziraphale had fallen. A long time ago in fact. It had happened slowly, then all at once. A gaze. A touch. A reassuring embrace when the world seemed to crumble before him.

Book: Crowley sauntered
Show: David Tennant becomes a human pendulum with his hips

Heaven: You can't be with Crowley anymore!

Aziraphale: Okay Yeets himself down

Heaven: You can’t meet with Crowley anymore! 
Aziraphale: I’m going to do what’s called  a pro gamer move 

I love the start of Crowley carrying him to the sofa and HEY YOU GOT HIS WALKING RIGHT

When I saw Aziraphale's half-black wings, I was almost expecting to see Crowley rise, and Rise, up to catch him, so they both be half-fallen with black-white wings. Not disappointed though. This was fantastic.
description:
An alternate timeline in which Aziraphale falls in order to feel safe meeting with Crowley.
